        • passButton

          javax.swing.JButton passButton
          Used in the beginning of the game. Passes the card, not declaring trump.

        • pickupButton

          javax.swing.JButton pickupButton
          Used in the beginning of the game. Tells the dealer to pick up the card, declaring trump. Is placed on the board as a clickable card.

        • tablePanel

          javax.swing.JPanel tablePanel
          Holds all the components for the current cards in play. Along with other players cards.

        • cardsPanel

        • infoPanel

        • scoreLabel

          Holds the current round points and over all score information.

        • alertLabel

          javax.swing.JLabel alertLabel
          Is used to notify the player about the game state.

        • trumpLabel

          Tells the player which suit is trump.

        • beginningPhase

          boolean beginningPhase
          Denotes that the game is in the phase of choosing trump.
